<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="#" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href='https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="CSS/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <a href="#" class="logo"></a>

        <div class="nav">
            <a href="#home">Home</a>
            <a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
        </div>

        <div class="nav-responsive">
            <a href="#home">Home</a>
            <a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a>
            <a href="#about">About</a>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-hamburguer">
            <div class="bar1">
                <div class="bar2">
                    <div class="bar3"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </header>

    <section class="home" id="home">
        <div class="home-content">
            <h1>André Bianchi</h1>
            <h3>Software <span>Developer</span></h3>

            <div class="social-media">

                <a href="mailto:nikumu@engineer.com">
                    <i class='bx bx-envelope'></i>
                </a>

                <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/nikumu">
                    <i class='bx bxl-linkedin'></i>
                </a>

                <a title="Bluesky" href="https://bsky.app/profile/nikumu.com">
                    <img height="28" width="28" style="color:red;" src="https://cdn.simpleicons.org/bluesky/4493f8" />
                </a>

                <a href="https://t.me/nekonikumu">
                    <i class='bx bxl-telegram'></i>
                </a>

            </div>

            <div>
                <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1SQsZRZD3dDjJAkZ1X__cUM60RA2iuQLq/view?usp=drive_link"
                    class="btn">Download CV</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="home-img">
            <img src="img/Profile.png" alt="Profile picture">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="portfolio" id="portfolio">
        <h2>Latest <span>Projects</span></h2>

        <div class="portfolio-container">
            <div class="portfolio-box">
                <img src="img/30-days-of-js.png" alt="Portfolio 1">

                <div class=" portfolio-layer">
                    <h4>30 Days of JS</h4>

                    <p>
                        A collection of projects created during the 30 Days of Code challenge.
                    </p>

                    <a href="https://github.com/nikumu/30-days-of-js"><i class='bx bx-link-external'></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="portfolio-box">
                <img src="img/the-final-brain-cell.png" alt="Portfolio 3">

                <div class="portfolio-layer">
                    <h4>The Final Brain Cell</h4>

                    <p>
                        Game based on a guessing system, where the player has a limited number of attempts to guess a
                        random number.
                    </p>

                    <a href="https://github.com/nikumu/the-final-brain-cell/"><i class='bx bx-link-external'></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="portfolio-box">
                <img src="img/github-user-info.png" alt="Portfolio 5">

                <div class="portfolio-layer">
                    <h4>Github User Info</h4>

                    <p>
                        The project retrieves and presents detailed information about any GitHub user using the GitHub
                        API.
                    </p>

                    <a href="https://github.com/nikumu/github-user-info"><i class='bx bx-link-external'></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about" id="about">
        <div class="about-content">
            <h3>About Me</h3>

            <p>
                Sou desenvolvedor web front-end com mais de 2 anos de experiência criando sites dinâmicos e visualmente
                atraentes. Especializo-me em criar interfaces intuitivas e fáceis de usar, utilizando tecnologias como
                HTML, CSS e
                JavaScript, além de frameworks modernos, como React e Angular. Minha paixão por um código limpo e
                eficiente me motiva a
                aprender continuamente e incorporar os avanços mais recentes no desenvolvimento web
            </p>

            <a href="#" class="btn">Read More</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <!-- <p>Copyright &copy; 2024 by &lt;/Nikumu&gt;</p> -->
        <p>Copyright &copy; 2024 by Nikumu</p>
    </footer>
</body>
<script src="js/script.js"></script>

</html>
